      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Primary typeface for all display, heading, body, and UI text. Weight 300 at 60-72px is anti-conventional — most platforms use 600-700 for hero text; the thin weight creates authority through mass (huge scale) rather than stroke weight. Weight 380 handles body and subheadings. Weight 570 for labels and small UI. Custom font unavailable externally."
